skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fuel economy
des:
It's a simple converter app for a fuel usage

You can ask to convert miles per gallon to liters per 100 kilometers or vice versa.

Example:

Alexa, ask fuel economy to convert 55 mpg to liters per hundred kilometers

Alexa, ask fuel economy to convert 24 miles per gallon to liters per hundred kilometers

Alexa, ask fuel economy to convert 10 liters per hundred kilometers to mpg

Alexa, ask fuel economy to convert 13 liters per hundred kilometers to miles per gallon
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
